Hello, I'm Rias!

If you want to invite me on your server use this link: %invite%.

I am based on modules and submodules with commands. You can type `r!modules` to see the list with all modules. You can use `r!commands module` or `r!commands submodule` to see a list of all of the commands in that module or submodule. For information about a command, use `r!h command`
 To see the list with all commands use `r!allcmds`.

Rias Support Server: %creatorServer%.
